			<td class="cs8B10DF83" colspan="4" valign="top"><p class="cs1DE97462"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;17. RECOMMENDED CHILD SUPPORT ORDER (Subtract smaller amount on line 16 from larger amount on line 16. Parent with larger amount on line 16 owes the other parent the difference.)</span></p></td><td class="csC825E270" valign="top"><p class="cs1DE97462"><span class="csEF05ACC">$</span></p></td><td class="cs633F7D8" colspan="3" valign="top"><p class="cs1DE97462"><span class="csEF05ACC">$</span></p></td><td class="cs6CC5E414" colspan="2" valign="top"><p class="cs1DE97462"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p></td></tr>
